        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Concerning lead.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Mr Peter W Love</persName></p>

<p>Be so good as to send me word by <persName>Mr Moses Bates</persName> whether the Lead
on <persName>Mr Wilkenson</persName> by <persName>Hartshorn and White</persName> can be had should a
Cart be sent on the <date when="1811-06-08">morrow </date>As I am truly distress for Lead to make
out my Boat load&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName>    [Rubric]</p>

<p><placeName>Durham Hall</placeName> <placeName>Mine A Burton</placeName> <date when="1811-06-07">June 7 1811</date> [Addressed] <persName>Mr
Peter W Love</persName>   <placeName>Mine   <hi rend="italic">Shibboleth</hi></placeName></p>

        </div1>
    </body>
